April 3, which allows either party to walk away with no further obligation.=
 Often in circumstances like this =E2=80=94=C2=A0where both sides want to g=
et the deal done, but it has been delayed by =E2=80=9Ca variety of reasons =
outside of the parties=E2=80=99 control=E2=80=9D =E2=80=94=C2=A0the parties=
