s able to drive a hard bargain for the extension. =E2=80=9CSure we=E2=80=99=
ll extend the drop-dead date, but in exchange you have to double the price.=
=E2=80=9D I like it! In the February 2022=C2=A0market for SPACs, and for cr=
ypto, a hot crypto company is going to have a lot more negotiating leverage=
